@SHORTDESC:	Convert **kern pitch to a base-7 integer.
@LONGDESC:	Convert **kern pitch to a base-7 integer.
	This is a diatonic pitch class with C=0, D=1, ..., B=6.
	

@@BEGIN: EXAMPLE
@DESCRIPTION:
@CODE:
